{
  "stem": "7302.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was two days, you have to keep up-- Shabbos and Sunday.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was everything closed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Shabbos was everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when the Russians came up, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They interfered.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm talking about when we had been in Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I have been alone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't-- they didn't teach in Shabbos and Sunday, anyways.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't have courses.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's two days, it wasn't any courses.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So who knew if I kept it up or not.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I have been the only one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- I have done what I wanted to do, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's not, I have to go to the shul or something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I met my husband.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We have been-- not engaged-- but we have been going together.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We kept in touch when I have been away in letters.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He's from the same street-- not only city-- from the same street.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We hadn't been so close when this started, but before the war, about three years or four years, we started to go, like, steady, like they saying here.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I have been away, we just are sending letters from each other.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I came, he used to take me to school and pick me up, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one night, we went there, came home, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it started, the war.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then the Russian people was going to all the houses, saying, run away, run away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Go to the woods.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were heading like the river, I told you, and then the woods.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And like, up street was a long, long street, and ended with a bridge.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you passed the bridge, there was the woods.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We went to the woods.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't tell you this story.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
